subjects = set([])
sessions = Navigate.getSessions(BRAIN_VOL_FILES, PROJECT_URI)
for s in sessions:
    acquisitions = Navigate.getAcquisitions(BRAIN_VOL_FILES, s)
    for acq in acquisitions:
        sub = Navigate.getSubject(BRAIN_VOL_FILES, acq)
        assert sub != None
        subjects.add(sub)
assert len(subjects) > 5
